{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"28b5a32ff4","title":"关于共产党对三民主义的态度问题的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9e3694d443","index":0,"year":1938,"month":5,"day":3,"articleId":"28b5a32ff4"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji12","name":"毛泽东全集第12卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji12.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji12":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8eae757e35","type":"paragraph","text":"关于共产党对三民主义的","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"28b5a32ff4"},{"id":"fe4b7d215e","type":"paragraph","text":"态度问题的讲话！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"28b5a32ff4"},{"id":"49cbdb702e","type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年5月3日）去年九月二十二日发表的《中共中央为公布国共合作宣言》，表明了中共对三民主义的态度，即“孙中山先生的三民主义为今日中国之必需，本党愿为其彻底的实现而奋斗”。中共提出的抗日救国十大纲领本质上是三民主义的。中共愿同国民党一道，在统一战线抗日第一的原则下实行三民主义。三民主义是实现社会主义和共产主义的必经之路11这是毛泽东在执大第三期第二大队关于共产党对三民主义的态度问题讲话的一部分。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"28b5a32ff4"}],"page":{"id":"c6c5897079","publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"28b5a32ff4","start":177,"end":177}}}},"__N_SSG":true}